general: @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Barlow+Condensed'); @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Fauna+One'); #gitViewModule{background-color: #111; color: #EEE; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; background-color:white; border-radius:5px; margin: 20px;} #gitViewModule div{background-color: #CCC; color:black; margin: 5px; border-radius: 3px; padding: 10px; overflow-y: auto; overflow-x: hidden; position: relative;}
title: .repoName{font-family: 'Fauna One', serif; font-size: 2em; text-align: center;}
contributions: .commitCount{display:inline-block; margin-right:30px;} .commitCount label{font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.2em;} .contribution label{ font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em;} .commitCount span{ font-weight: bolder; font-size: 2.3em;} .contribution span{ font-weight: bolder; font-size: 2.3em;}
